This archive is intended as a file-replacement patch.

Use either:
1) Copy CMakeLists.txt from this archive to:
   D:\MEDIA\Desktop\jitsi-ndi-native\CMakeLists.txt

or:
2) Run apply_cmake_patch.ps1 from PowerShell.

The replacement keeps this link line:
   target_link_libraries(jitsi-ndi-native PRIVATE avcodec avutil swscale swresample)

Do not install ffmpeg[avutil] through vcpkg: avutil is a library to link, not a vcpkg feature.
